---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="The History of Me — hkg">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <a
      href="/about"
      class="mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
    >
      <svg
        class="h-3.5 w-3.5"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
      >
        <path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"></path>
        <path d="M19 12H5"></path>
      </svg>
      back
    </a>

    <div class="mt-8 mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-1">The History of H</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Hello my name is Haroon I was born in the early 00's in Reston, Virginia. I come
        from two loving parents who started at opposite ends of the world and met one another
        in the states. Born and raised in the states, although I go back to the motherland
        (Egypt) often.
      </p>
      <p>
        Thrown into the public education system which had its run but now that's over
        thankfully. Traveled half the globe with family. Curated the most diverse and truly
        interesting circles of friends that challenge me to learn and grow every day. Currently, I'm
        surrounded by go-getters and really just the most ambitious people ever, which I
        wouldn't give up for the world.
      </p>
      <p>
        My current passions are psychology/moral philosophy, physical wellness, building
        really insane ideas, and of course, business.
      </p>
      <p>
        My biggest goal in life is to experience all that there is to experience and I truly
        believe that I'm on that path to self actualization.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
